<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{% block title %}Invasion Timer!{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon.ico"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u"
          crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{{ asset('css/style.css') }}">
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
<div id="fullpage">
    <div class="section " id="section0">
        <div style="display:table;width:100%;height:100%;">
            <div style="display:table-cell;vertical-align:middle;">
                <div style="text-align:center;"><img src="/img/legion.png"></div>
                <div style="text-align:center;" id="message">{{ message }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section" id="section2">
        <div style="display:table;width:100%;height:100%;">
            <div style="display:table-cell;vertical-align:middle;padding:10%;">
                <h1>Qu'est-ce qu'une invasion ?</h1>
                <p>Une invasion c'est lorsque l'une des zones des îles brisées est temporairement attaquées par la
                    Legion. Elle dure 6h, toutes les 12h30.</p>
                <p>Les expéditions de la zone envahie sont remplacés par des expéditions spécifiques. Une
                    quête est disponible au niveau 110 et demande d'accomplir
                    4 de ces expéditions pour débloquer un scénario, octroyant loots et éclats de néant.</p>
                <p>
                    De plus, les expéditions de l'invasion sont disponibles à partir du niveau 98, et permettent de gagner de
                    l'expérience.
                </p>
                <h1>What is an invasion?</h1>
                <p>An invasion is when zones in the Broken Isles are attacked by the Legion. It lasts 6h, and is available every 12h30.</p>
                <p>
                    What it does: it replaces the world quest of the zone, with specific world quests.
                    Furthermore, a quest is available at level 110 where you need to complete 4 of this world quest to unlock a scenario, which give loots and nethershards.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Moreover, the world quests of the invasion are available at level 98, which give to the player a quick way to gain
                    experience.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="hidden-inputs">
    <input type="hidden" name="textInvasionIsOn" value="{{ textInvasionIsOn }}">
    <input type="hidden" name="textNextInvasion" value="{{ textNextInvasion }}">
    <input type="hidden" name="timestampDefault" value="{{ timestampDefault }}">
    <input type="hidden" name="timeInterval" value="{{ timeInterval }}">
    <input type="hidden" name="durationInvasion" value="{{ durationInvasion }}">
</div>
<script
        src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.js"
        integrity="sha256-DZAnKJ/6XZ9si04Hgrsxu/8s717jcIzLy3oi35EouyE="
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('js/moment.js') }}"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('js/jquery.fullPage.min.js') }}"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ asset('js/main.js') }}"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $('#fullpage').fullpage({
            anchors: ['timing', 'whatIsIt'],
            sectionsColor: ['#555', '#3c0600'],
            scrollBar: true
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>